  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">BI - Food Crisis Response Development Policy Grant</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The objective of the grant is to help the Government of Burundi in reducing hunger, preventing an increase in poverty and social unrest, and ensuring the fiscal stability needed to foster medium-term social and economic development.  The supported policy measures include suspension of custom duties and taxes on basic food items and expansion of food aid, social assistance and related programs.</narrative>
  </description>
